{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b04294edf6","title":"毛泽东转发薄一波关于上海市五反准备工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2501f4e578","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"b04294edf6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6d1eed553b","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发薄一波关于上海市五反准备工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"d7d8694e3f","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"03af029831","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"fb19ae1d97","type":"paragraph","text":"此件发各中央局转各城市市委参考。在任何城市进行五反，必须分析情况，确定策略，组织工人、组织干部（工作队）、组织指挥机关，并做出全盘计划，方能真正开展五反斗争，并在斗争中不断修改自己的计划，决不能盲目地进行五反。市委须每天指导各区，几天总结一次经验。各中央局分局省市区党委须几天讨论当地五反工作一次，决不能满足于只发一二个原则指示。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"634a1aec92","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东三月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"b8b89785f2","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"d154a8e57e","type":"paragraph","text":"应按中央新的划分标准，划分为守法的、基本守法的、半违法半守法的、严重违法的和完全违法的五类。——毛注","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"7f4ce3dd6b","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"089eb86ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"不应当提出反暴利的口号。——毛注","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"4ca4a24369","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"050905687b","type":"paragraph","text":"此两项应当反，可以归入反盗窃国家资财一类。——毛注","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"638794927d","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"242e79eef7","type":"paragraph","text":"大城市和中等城市不同，必须以区为五反的单位，市则统一领导各区。——毛注","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"14b05c616d","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"},{"id":"e6f8ae4f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"严密控制，非常需要。有些城市控制不严，出了乱子。——毛注","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6"}],"page":{"id":"54a014c97e","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b04294edf6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}